name: Unidentified_Zabrak_Dark_Jedi
content:
A Zabrak Dark Jedi was a female who was sensitive to the Force, and eventually turned to the dark side. At some point during the Galactic Civil War between the Galactic Empire and the Alliance to Restore the Republic, she engaged at least three B2 super battle droids in combat, using her lightsaber to fight the droids. During the skirmish, the Dark Jedi executed a 360-degree spin  and bisected  the battle droids horizontally. She was pale-skinned and had red, flowing hair. The Zabrak woman wore a cape and red-colored clothing, and used a curved-hilt lightsaber with a red crystal.
The Zabrak Dark Jedi was depicted on the card "Sai Tok Jung Ma" from the Squadrons Over Corellia expansion set of the Star Wars Galaxies Trading Card Game, released in 2008. She was drawn by Mark Evans.
